@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
title Project Coherent Storage - S3/Object REST Translator
left to right direction
actor "S3 client\nawscli/SDK/rclone" as S3C
actor "REST client\nSDK/SwaggerUI" as RESTC
rectangle "Translator services" {
  component "s3_net_service\nHTTP 8080" as S3NET
  component "meta_translate_service\nHTTP 9000" as META
  component "rest_net_service\nHTTP 8000" as RESTNET
  component "metrics_exporter\nPrometheus 9100" as METRICS
}
rectangle "Backend adapters" {
  database "Object adapter" as OBJ
  database "KV adapter" as KV
  database "Vector/ANN adapter" as VEC
  database "Prefix-cache adapter\nUnified + dimensional indexed" as PFX
  database "Metadata DB\nredacted audit modes" as MDB
}
S3C --> S3NET : S3 HTTP\nPUT/GET/HEAD/LIST/MULTIPART
RESTC --> RESTNET : REST HTTP\nobject/KV/vector/prefix-cache
S3NET --> META : normalized S3 envelope
META --> RESTNET : mapped REST command
RESTNET --> META : REST response
META --> S3NET : S3-shaped status/XML/headers
RESTNET --> OBJ : /objects/{bucket}/{key}
RESTNET --> KV : /kv/{namespace}/{key}
RESTNET --> VEC : /vectors/{namespace} + /search
RESTNET --> PFX : /prefix-cache/{mode}/.../prefixes/{prefix_id}
META --> MDB : mapping metadata by mode
S3NET ..> METRICS
META ..> METRICS
RESTNET ..> METRICS
note bottom of PFX
Exact put/get/delete require prefix_id.
Search/invalidate are collection actions.
No OpenZFS, DPU, RDMA, CXL, or VLAN identifiers leak to clients.
end note
@enduml
